short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Set of helper functions for MyJysk

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Several improvements for better MyJysk user experience:
- Add "quick assign to" buttons (for Tickets)
- Track ticket subscriptions
- (Optionally) remove unused\less frequently used buttons (for Tickets)
- (Optionally) add ticket description text in tickets list
